    <briefdescription>
<para>Generic Model API - Model-agnostic interface for CK-Engine. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>All generated models emit the same function names, making the inference engine completely model-agnostic. To use different models, compile separate binaries.</para>
<para>Usage: void *model = <ref refid="ck__model__api_8h_1a2f39a0720a1075cc9d3c25fc322ff1b3" kindref="member">ck_model_create()</ref>; ck_model_load_weights(model, &quot;weights.bump&quot;); ck_model_forward(model, tokens, num_tokens); // prefill ck_model_decode(model, &amp;token, token_index); // decode float *logits = ck_model_get_logits(model); ck_model_free(model); </para>
    </detaileddescription>
